caption.p:
Malondialdehyde (MDA) levels in the liver tissues (nmol/mg) of the control and experimental rats. Data analyzed using one-way ANOVA. Values are expressed as mean ± SEM.
a
p < 0.05 between the normal control (C) and diabetic control (D).
b
p < 0.05 between the diabetic control (D)and diabetic TL treatment (D + TL).
c
p < 0.05 between the normal control (C) and the normal TL treatment (C + TL).
d
p < 0.05 between the normal TL treatment (C + TL) and diabetic TL treatment (D + TL).
